data.description: Discover the perfect blend of historic charm and contemporary comfort in this beautifully renovated gem, ideally located on the of the most sought-after streets downtown. With easy access to top -notch amenities, this property offers an enviable lifestyle. Every inch of this home has been meticulously restored with modern upgrades, including new electrical and plumbing, professionally designed bathrooms and kitchen. Relax and entertain on the gracious front porch, where you can enjoy the sunsets and soak up the charm of this historic neighborhood. Notably, the first floor remained unaffected during Florence since the home is elevated. Renowned local contractor Tar Heel Builders, in collaboration with the professionally trained decorator, oversaw the restoration process, ensuring that the home's historic character was preserved while introducing contemporary comforts. This home is a true testament to the dedication of its owners, evident in the pristine condition and attention to every detail. From the original fixtures to the gleaming hardwood floors, it exudes the rich history and unique personality of the area's Historic District. Don't miss this chance to own a piece of history in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in town. Experience the charm and elegance of this beautifully restored home, where history meets modern living.There is off street parking and a full first floor bath!
